\N<Ryuda Soldier>The people of this town are lucky. There are places that
have been massacred without question. Be thankful to Lord
Zuuteruka.
<ActiveMessage:\C[1]■EV発生■>

\N<Rozaro>Segi-san, were you at the management office? Could it be
about your next opponent?
\N<Segi>...Yes. As you surmised.

\N<Rozaro>Hmm... If it's alright with you, could you tell me more
about your opponent? I'd like to offer whatever little help
I can.
\N<Segi>Yes, I'd be glad to.

\N<Rozaro>The death row inmate Zozoie... I see, so he's the next one
to face Segi-san.
\N<Segi>Yes... You already knew about him?

\N<Rozaro>Ah, he's quite infamous in certain circles. I heard he was
once the leader of a band of bandits... A man who wouldn't
choose means for his ends, like a beast.

\N<Rozaro>Moreover, he's said to be extremely skilled. Rumor has it
that countless have fallen to his blade.
\N<Segi>...

\N<Rozaro>...I apologize. I didn't mean to make you anxious with what
I said.

\N<Segi>Hehe, it's okay. I was prepared for this when I decided to
join the training soldiers' meeting.

\N<Rozaro>...I see. Still, it's not wise to go into battle without a
plan. We must prepare some sort of countermeasure.
A

\N<Woman>It's widely rumored that not a single plant remains where
the people of Ryuda have passed...

\N<Woman>Of course, it's probably a rumor that's been exaggerated,
but even so, I worry about the future of this town...

\N<Man>The management office over there used to be quite literally
the nerve center of the city.

\N<Man>Well... now it's completely turned into the administrative
governing body for the Ryuda troops stationed in this
town...

\N<Ryuda Soldier>Inside, you'll find the town's garrison commander, Lord
Zuuteruka. Be very careful about how you speak.

\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Heh, heh... that was fun... I talked a lot with Rame-chan
just now...
\N<Fubii>Hey there. Good afternoon. What are you doing here?
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Ah...!?

\N<Fubii>Ahaha, don't be so scared. We're friends... comrades, aren't
we?
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>C-comrades...? You and me...?

\N<Fubii>That's right. Isn't that so? We're comrades who attend the
same training school, right?
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>U... yeah.

\N<Fubii>See? So, as a comrade, I have something important to discuss
with you.

\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Something important...? What is it... what do you want with
me...?

\N<Fubii>You see, lately... you've been getting along well with Riia
and Rame. Why is that?
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Why you ask... they helped me from you guys... ah...!?

\N<Fubii>Ahaha, it's okay, don't worry about it. After all, we're
friends now. But even if we say friends? That's not
something you can have infinitely, right?

\N<Fubii>So... right? Riia and Rame, and then me. It's obvious who
would be more beneficial to be friends with, isn't it?
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Eh...!?

\N<Fubii>Come to my side. If you do, I won't let anyone from the
training school lay a finger on you. I'll protect you.
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>But...
\N<Fubii>You like Rame, don't you?
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>That's not...!

\N<Fubii>It's okay, no need to hide it. She's cute, isn't she? If you
become my friend, I'll let you have her.
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Have her... like... eh...?

\N<Fubii>I mean I'll let you do as you please with her. Of course,
every inch of her body... you know?
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Rame-chan's... body...

\N<Fubii>Well, it won't be for free though. In exchange, I want you
to find some dirt on Riia's aunt. Something that will make
it impossible for her to oppose me.
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Riia's mom's...? How am I supposed to...?

\N<Fubii>I'll leave that up to you. It will mean betraying Riia, but
then her aunt might become obedient to me too. That would be
just perfect for you, wouldn't it?
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>That is...

\N<Fubii>Ahaha, looks like we've come to an agreement. I'm looking
forward to it, okay?
A
